data.Name: Matan Zohar
data.Bio: UK born, Matan Zohar (aka Mat Zo, Reif, Unripelemon), still a teenager, has made a sudden appearence on the EDM scene. After 3 years of producing varied electronic music, ranging from Drum and Bass to Trance, he discovered Progressive House. This discovery lead him to being trcklisted by some of the worlds top DJs. But still a teenager, Mat Zo is at the beginning of a long career.
